name: Flattered by Love
description:
Four eyes is not enough if we couldn't feel the love. To love or to be loved is just a story of how human life. It's always possible if we live in a world full of hate and sin but to feel the love is another story. Love could bring and sin can also brings love. We're just living in a world full of anarchy with a love as the spise in between.

We choose our love, we choose our sin.
